HEADWORD: Silverite
<hw>Sil"ver*ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who favors the
use or establishment of silver as a monetary standard; -- so called by
those who favor the gold standard.</def> <mark>[Colloq. or
Cant]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

